{"tid":1497984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教你對付監控攝影機","createTime":"2019-08-23T08:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T10:57:42.000Z","uid":154277,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"740701934bd2f449e983603d15923239ac43c2ed","tid":1497984,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:12:45.000Z","msg":"示威的時候，路上的監控攝影機會用容貌辯識攝影機監察示威者。黑警也會拍攝勇武示威者，根據他們衣著和外表特徵，日後用這些影片進行檢控。<br />\n<br />\n要對付這些攝影機一點都不困難。對付容貌辯識監察攝影機的最好方法是<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在紙牌上貼上很多容貌照片</span></span></strong>，例如販民議員的競選海報和報章上剪下來的照片，只要有手掌大小的頭部照片就足夠。當很多示威者舉起貼上大量容貌照片的紙牌，容貌辯認系統會超過負荷，失去功能，甚至全線檔機。<br />\n<br />\n對付近距離攝影的最佳方法是<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有人穿上一模一樣的螢光條背心</span></span></strong>。口罩和頭盔上也貼上螢光貼。在光線照亮之下，這些螢光條會令到攝影機的光圈收縮，其他東西都暗淡無光。這麼差的影片不能用作呈堂證據。<br />\n<br />\n示威者用繩縛著螢光棒一端，不停高速轉動形成光盾，也可以在晚上干擾拍攝。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/yeungwailung/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fyeungwailung%2Fposts%2F&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1U9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=57cbad58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/yeungwailung/posts/</a>"},{"pid":"2068db1f9c92686843002959957382090928049d","tid":1497984,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:13:52.000Z","msg":"警方已向 824「燃點香港&middot;全民覺醒」觀塘遊行集會活動發出不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n路線為：駿業街遊樂場&gt;駿業街&gt;海濱道&gt;順業街&gt;偉業街&gt;常怡道&gt;宏照道&gt;零碳天地外<br />\n<br />\n詳情將會稍後透過KT tg channel 發放：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">「燃點香港&middot;全民覺醒」</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">五大訴求、缺一不可</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">智能燈柱、侵犯私穩</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>日期：24/8/2019<br />\n時間：1300集會、1330遊行、1600解散<br />\n集會地點：駿業街遊樂場<br />\n遊行起點：駿業街遊樂場</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公海： <a href=\"http://t.me/kt824discuss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkt824discuss&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1U9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=d8df86e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/kt824discuss</a><br />\n<br />\n資料發佈： <a href=\"http://t.me/kt824info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkt824info&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1U9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=e0a0e5d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/kt824info</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣： <a href=\"http://t.me/kt824promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkt824promo&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1U9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=b3635217\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/kt824promo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbBYwct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbBYwct.jpg&h=cabbffda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f27529a5c766c36b79180373c1709f3d9adbee00","tid":1497984,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:14:16.000Z","msg":"823 香港之路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae43834d6ef6ba4009e5a3e9ed8bb5c5f485150","tid":1497984,"uid":269221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:15:17.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"b420d8f4060a944969bacfeab5d43552bd8d10e2","tid":1497984,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:44:22.000Z","msg":"用強光照鏡頭呢？電筒唔算犯法"},{"pid":"651e0e682f21dbb044fc3ead22e8eb198d958cc3","tid":1497984,"uid":25797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:45:44.000Z","msg":"貼啲藍絲出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3394575c621e78d14304f243b934124c9b6